## ‚ö° Quick Start

### Clone This Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/narayannikhil/Dockerizing_node_project-.git
cd Dockerizing_node_project-
```

### Run Any Project
```bash
# Navigate to project
cd Basic_node_server

# Build image
docker build -t my-app .

# Run container
docker run -p 3000:3000 my-app

# Visit http://localhost:3000
```

